      h2 The Place to Come for Enterprise Java
    .large-8.column
      p Red Hat JBoss® Enterprise Application Platform 6 provides an innovative modular, cloud-ready architecture, powerful management and automation, and world class developer productivity. It is Java™ EE 6 certified and features powerful yet flexible management, improved performance and scalability, and many new features to maximize developer productivity. It builds on the community foundation of WildFly.

