      asciidoc:  
		 Work alongside smart, motivated people to apply your skills toward a bigger effort. Look at the link:http://javaee-samples.github.io/[Java EE 7 Samples Project] or contribute to link:https://github.com/jboss-developer/www.jboss.org[JBoss Developer] and don't forget to find solutions in our link:http://www.jboss.org/forums/[Forums].
    .large-12.column
      h4 Getting Started Is Easy
      asciidoc:   
		Find all you need in the link:http://www.jboss.org/products/eap/get-started/[Getting Started Section] on JBoss developer. It's not much more than just hitting download and unzip into a folder of your choice. And we also provide link:http://www.jboss.org/products/eap/learn[learning resources] and link:http://www.redhat.com/en/services/training[training] to improve your skills, or the skills of your team, with our hands-on, role-based training for IT professionals and developers. If you feel the need for latest innovation and specifications, you need to look at link:http://wildfly.org/[WildFly]. This is the community version and helps you build flexible and lightweight applications.
    .large-6.column
