	asciidoc:     
		There are many resources available for link:http://www.jboss.org/products/eap/overview/[JBoss EAP] on link:http://www.jboss.org[JBoss Developer] or the link:http://access.redhat.com[Red Hat Customer Portal]. You can also follow our Developer Advocates link:http://blog.arungupta.me[Arun Gupta] or link://blog.eisele.net[Markus Eisele] and see, what they have to share.

